_:N369c59ddb0ab45d2a74f6f7646c6cc26 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Chris Grigg is Chair of the National Wealth Fund and of Evelyn Partners, the wealth management company. He was also appointed non-executive Chair for Melrose plc, the aerospace company, in March 2025.</p>\n\n<p>In his executive career, Chris was most recently <abbr title=\"Chief Executive Officer\">CEO</abbr> of British Land. Before that, he was <abbr title=\"Chief Executive Officer\">CEO</abbr> of Barclays Commercial Bank. Chris’s earlier career was spent at Goldman Sachs, where he was a Partner, and at Morgan Grenfell. Chris has an <abbr title=\"Master of Arts\">MA</abbr> in Economics from the University of Cambridge.</p>\n\n" .
